例规定生育子女的夫妻，除国家规定的产假外，女职工增加六十日产假，配偶享受不少于十五日陪产假，三周岁以下婴幼儿父母各享受每年累计不少于十日育儿假。 自去年中央宣布实行三孩生育政策后，各地也纷纷出台生育支持政策。据第一财经记者统计，目前已有 30 个省份完成人口与计划生育条例修订。同时，据不完全统计，目前已至少有 18 个省份出台了实施方案。从现有情况看，各地普遍延长产假 30~90 天，增加普惠托育服务发展、计划生育家庭权益保障等条款。 来源：第一财经"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-45b3c0d47f324270e5504417b1c8d3dc_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/546272937"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhIzpx+vR+q50EAMaCDgzNjc3MTM1IOKxmZcGMBU4wwJAMHIJNTQ2MjcyOTM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1659362956.0879836", "card_id": "Q_537512874", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 127}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人到中年，你活成了自己喜欢的模样吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "人到中年，面临上有老下有小，房贷债务的巨大压力下，谁的生活不是一地鸡毛？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fb198e903d8548bd200fdb64ffdf91df_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/537512874"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhIzpx+vR+q50EAMaCDgxNzI5MTcxIN6InJUGMAA4uwJAMXIJNTM3NTEyODc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15}